description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Jumping Cat
-The Triple Pagoda and the Cat
-Okinawa's Scenery and the Cat
-Hide and Seek
-Japanese School Girl Who Loves a Cat
-Cat and Monk
-Street Cat in Onomichi, Hiroshima
-Cats in the Harbor
-Cat napping on the Wall
-Downtown Cat
name: Street Cats in Japan
